  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select your favorite Brainrot characters and watch them fight in a simulated battle ⚔️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/62f9ad04932dcaa0256220abc3db6f5a.webp?t=1749022574\" width=50 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/fdf28127f56f0b46ae4f0a481705d48d.poster.avif?t=1749022574\" width=150 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/fdf28127f56f0b46ae4f0a481705d48d.webm?t=1749022574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/fdf28127f56f0b46ae4f0a481705d48d.mp4?t=1749022574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/2209436b4442a236c1ce3cf468335eac.avif?t=1749022574\" width=200 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/33f66f2da4e295bf0ee31ead24e87854.poster.avif?t=1749022574\" width=150 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/33f66f2da4e295bf0ee31ead24e87854.webm?t=1749022574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/33f66f2da4e295bf0ee31ead24e87854.mp4?t=1749022574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real time battle simulation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unrestricted team creation (as many teams with as many fighters as you want)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedural battle environements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlimited characters per team</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom character creation and Workshop support to share them</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your unique battles, with unlimited combinations and possibilities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are talking 1v1, 5v1, and multiple teams such as 4v3v6v2, 20v20v20 or whatever you can imagine 💥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/7eafe689c44212e85a641798bbc2913f.poster.avif?t=1749022574\" width=300 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/7eafe689c44212e85a641798bbc2913f.webm?t=1749022574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/7eafe689c44212e85a641798bbc2913f.mp4?t=1749022574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/0300c834506d2ffd58fa16e3b2716f94.poster.avif?t=1749022574\" width=300 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/0300c834506d2ffd58fa16e3b2716f94.webm?t=1749022574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3726700/extras/0300c834506d2ffd58fa16e3b2716f94.mp4?t=1749022574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autopla